==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Trunkfish
<hw>Trunk"fish`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of several species of plectognath fishes, belonging to the
genus <gen>Ostracion</gen>, or the family <fam>Ostraciontidae</fam>,
having an angular body covered with a rigid integument consisting of
bony scales. Some of the species are called also <stype>coffer
fish</stype>, and <stype>boxfish</stype>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trunkful</ent>⟦br⟧
